\setlength{\parskip}{1.5ex}

We would like to submit the attached manuscript, ``Aspect-oriented RTL HW design using SystemC'', for
consideration for possible publication in the \emph{Microprocessors and Microsystems: Embedded Hardware Design}.

In the manuscript, we describe a SystemC-based aspect-oriented approach for creating more reusable RTL hardware designs.
In summary, its main contributions are:

\begin{itemize}
\item It provides a comprehensive analysis of related work in the area of AOP applied to hardware design;
\item It describes an AOP-based method for designing synthesizable hardware components;  
the proposed mechanisms are based only on standard C++ features available on the SystemC synthesizable subset; 
\item It presents the design and implementation of real world case studies, which allowed us to elucidate the tradeoffs of AOP applied to hardware;
In our cases, we have increased the code reuse by about 33\% with a circuit area overhead of only 2\%.
\end{itemize}

